<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٢ في الأصل و<span class="c1">"س"</span> <span class="c1">"فليس"</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٣ في <span class="c1">"ص"</span> <span class="c1">"للنسك"</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>